snippet.title: Ice Cream Pachinly Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
Ken Pepe, the creator and voice actor for the character Ice Cream Pachinly, is here to tell you more details about gameplay!

Ice Cream Pachinly comes out on Steam July 19th!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2861050/Ice_Cream_Pachinly/
